Package: alfanous
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 ${python:Depends},
 python-qt4,
 python-alfanous,
 fonts-arabeyes,
 ttf-me-quran
Recommends: islamic-menus
Description: Quranic search engine (desktop application)
 Alfanous is a Quranic search engine offers simple and advanced
 search services in the whole information that Holy Qur’an contains.
 It is based on the modern approach of information retrieval to get a 
 good-stability and a high-speed search.
 .
 This package contains a desktop GUI for the search engine.

Package: python-alfanous
Section: python
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Description: Quranic search engine (Python API)
 Alfanous is a Quranic search engine offers simple and advanced
 search services in the whole information that Holy Qur’an contains.
 It is based on the modern approach of information retrieval to get a 
 good-stability and a high-speed search.
 .
 This package contains the Python API.
